<p dir="auto"><strong>Code coverage enablement decisions are blocked on architectural clarity.</strong> The team needs to decide if code coverage should be independent of CodeQL workflow setup for code quality. Without resolution by next week's EPD sync, design delivery timelines are at risk. <a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/tassia-sp/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/tassia-sp">@tassia-sp</a> <a href="https://www.figma.com/design/8gsIkUVp01HgzoAKa1C1Qb/Code-quality--test-coverage?node-id=45-10411&amp;p=f&amp;t=0h6BGXWdXwDlAHtx-11" rel="nofollow">[Questions doc]</a></p>
